  "comment": "MEGA-Lite introduces the NEW theatrical Colorlite Q120. With an IP65 rugged housing, this unit is the ideal lighting solution for indoor and outdoor applications.Featuring a 120W RGBW COB LED, it can create rich saturated colors that add a fascinating attribute to any utilization. Between the RGBW and WW 90+ High CRI, this innovative unit allow users to create true warm white, amber and bold color combinations, eliminating the need for gel replacements. With smooth transitional hues it provides designers with the ability to seamlessly alter any setting including theater, architectural, house of worship and even house lighting.",
